376
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,760
Per mercat que he anat, deu euros.

377
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,760
I m'he comprat uns mitjons.

378
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:12,760
Estaven de descompte.

379
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:14,760
Set euros. Encara portava

380
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:16,760
